# Zest environment variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in values.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Share storage backend (PRD §7)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Leave both vars unset (default) to use localStorage.
# In this mode share links only work in the same browser/device.
#
# To enable cross-device sharing via Vercel KV / Upstash REST:
#   1. Create a KV database in your Vercel project or at upstash.com.
#   2. Set VITE_SHARE_KV_URL to the REST base URL  (no trailing slash).
#   3. Set VITE_SHARE_KV_REST_API_TOKEN to the read-write token.
#
# The app will automatically switch to the KV backend when VITE_SHARE_KV_URL
# is present. No code changes required.

# VITE_SHARE_KV_URL=https://YOUR-KV.kv.vercel-storage.com
# VITE_SHARE_KV_REST_API_TOKEN=your-token-here
